---
title: Bavette Steak with Sweet Potato Jumble with Black Beans, Cilantro Lime Rice, Vegan Crema & Tortilla Chips
description: If you’re in the market for a hearty, filling vegan dinner, we’ve got just the thing. Earthy sautéed mushrooms and tomato are tossed with hearty black beans and served with a colorful combo of roasted sweet potato and red onion alongside zesty cilantro rice. It’s all drizzled with a luscious vegan crema, and tortilla chips on the side for crunchy contrast. Top with fresh cilantro, a squeeze of lime juice, and a drizzle of hot sauce to complete this satisfying plant-based plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64dd088bef3d37ebd501000f-4eced796.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64dd088bef3d37ebd501000f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/bavette-steak-with-sweet-potato-jumble-64dd088bef3d37ebd501000f
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: South America
nutrition:
  calories: 1330 kcal
  fat: 49 g
  saturated fat: 11 g
  carbohydrates: 171 g
  sugar: 16 g
